{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"I’ve been on a kick lately about saying no to things. Apparently I’ve been pushed to my limit and can’t handle anything else so everything is turning into a no. But I still feel like a jerk for saying no and I don’t like feeling like a jerk. I start to apologize for saying no when I really meant it."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/09-01-feeling-badly-about-saying-no"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/09-01-feeling-badly-about-saying-no","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-09-01T00:05:16-05:00"}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"platforms":[{"name":"Brunow","introducedAt":"2017.01.20"}],"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"title":"Feeling Badly About Saying No","modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"role":"collectionGroup","title":"Archive","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"role":"collection","title":"Brunow","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/brunow"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/B